ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugins.geometryvalidation

Class GeometryValidatorPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.plugins.geometryvalidation.GeometryValidatorPlugin

  • public class GeometryValidatorPlugin
extends Object
    The GeometryValidatorPlugin converts the geometry to the requested coordinate system and precision model. It then checks to see if the geometry Geometry.isSimple(), Geometry.isValid(), and calculates the MinimumClearance.getDistance().
    Author:
    Paul Austin
